3
00:01:34,519 --> 00:01:37,040
(Episode 15)

4
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,000
Your colleagues are starting to get suspicious.

5
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,319
Keep going on blind dates.

6
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,759
It's a robbery! Help! I've been robbed!

7
00:02:20,199 --> 00:02:21,879
Our girl is great.

8
00:02:22,090 --> 00:02:23,530
What are you so happy about?

9
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:26,039
So many things happened lately, but we knew nothing.

10
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:31,530
Shi Yi has been like that since young.

11
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:33,090
She keeps all the problems to herself.

12
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:36,280
Why are there bad people like that?

13
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:38,090
How could they frame Shi Yi like that?

14
00:02:38,090 --> 00:02:39,639
The person is so evil.

15
00:02:39,639 --> 00:02:40,719
That's right.

16
00:02:40,719 --> 00:02:43,719
That Hou Jue seemed like an educated man.

17
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:46,199
How could he be so coldhearted?

18
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:48,639
One word from the girlfriend and he sent Shi Yi away.

19
00:02:48,919 --> 00:02:50,520
Where is justice?

20
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:53,199
Don't worry, ma'am. I've looked for Mr. Hou.

21
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,719
I pressured him a little.

22
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:55,960
He has to know...

23
00:02:56,159 --> 00:02:58,520
that Shi Yi is not without help.

24
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,840
Moreover, I've already decided.

25
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,759
Even if the police don't solve the case in time,

26
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:04,520
I'm still going to take legal action...

27
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,319
to seek justice for Shi Yi.

28
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,039
Thank you, Lan Qi.

29
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,599
Don't mention it.

30
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,479
To be honest, I've always been a bit hesitant...

31
00:03:12,479 --> 00:03:14,159
about her becoming a bodyguard.

32
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,599
Not only is it risky,

33
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:18,319
but you also don't get any respect from the client.

34
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,360
When there's a problem, the bodyguard is held responsible.

35
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:23,800
You have to be willing to die as well as suffer.

36
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:25,960
Even though the pay is good,

37
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,280
but it's at the expense of your life.

38
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,479
Why bother?

39
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:32,759
But it's what Shi Yi loves to do.

40
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:33,919
If you want her to switch jobs,

41
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:35,120
she definitely won't agree.

42
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,439
How would we know if we didn't try?

43
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,199
Lan Qi.

44
00:03:45,599 --> 00:03:46,960
You're well-connected.

45
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,400
Can you do something about it?

46
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,840
Help Shi Yi look for a suitable job.

47
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,759
Yes.

48
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,719
How about this?

49
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:59,360
I think our company's Security Department...

50
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:00,800
is a good fit for her.

51
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,000
Based on her experience,

52
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,479
she can become a manager.

53
00:04:04,639 --> 00:04:07,080
Firstly, the income will not be less than a personal bodyguard.

54
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:09,039
And more importantly,

55
00:04:09,479 --> 00:04:11,280
it is way less risky.

56
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,319
- That's great. - That's great.

57
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,599
But Mr. Wu, ma'am,

58
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,439
we can't make the decision.

59
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:18,519
You have to ask for her opinion.

60
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:21,360
It's not right for us to impose our intention onto her.

61
00:04:22,610 --> 00:04:23,680
That's true.

62
00:04:25,050 --> 00:04:27,240
I know. I know you're frustrated.

63
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,519
But I promise you.

64
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:30,079
I will submit the design blueprint...

65
00:04:30,279 --> 00:04:32,360
within the contract period, okay?

66
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,199
As you know, we're short-staffed.

67
00:04:34,959 --> 00:04:36,319
Okay, that's all for now.

68
00:04:36,319 --> 00:04:37,319
Okay, bye.

69
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,319
Hey, Ms. Qian.

70
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:51,879
I'm sorry. I completely forgot.

71
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:55,759
I promise you. I'll be right there.

72
00:04:56,050 --> 00:04:57,199
Don't be mad.

73
00:04:58,759 --> 00:05:01,050
I'm dead meat.

74
00:05:19,519 --> 00:05:20,879
Hurry up and take it out.

75
00:05:23,199 --> 00:05:24,959
- Mr. Hou, I'll take these in. - No.

76
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:26,560
Wait for me outside.

77
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:38,480
- Wait for me inside. - Okay.

78
00:05:41,319 --> 00:05:42,319
Qian Qian.

79
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,240
I'm really sorry.

80
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,399
I'm late.

81
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:47,839
You're late on your first day of class.

82
00:05:48,439 --> 00:05:49,800
Do you really want to learn?

83
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:51,759
Qian Qian,

84
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:55,439
the way you spoke, looking all serious,

85
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:56,639
was so cool.

86
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:57,759
Don't joke around.

87
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,319
Do you want to learn?

88
00:06:00,879 --> 00:06:02,040
Of course I do.

89
00:06:02,319 --> 00:06:04,120
I promise it won't happen again.

90
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,519
Let's get started.

91
00:06:05,519 --> 00:06:06,519
No.

92
00:06:08,399 --> 00:06:10,279
If my team members were late today...

93
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:12,040
Of course they wouldn't be late.

94
00:06:12,439 --> 00:06:13,920
But let's say they were,

95
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,480
they'd receive punishment.

96
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,079
Running for 10,000m.

97
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,439
Running for 10,000m?

98
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:21,040
You're so ruthless.

99
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:25,639
I saw a garden outside on my way here.

100
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:27,560
It's about 1,200m per lap.

101
00:06:27,759 --> 00:06:28,759
You can do eight laps.

102
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:34,480
What?

103
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,560
Go on.

104
00:06:36,199 --> 00:06:37,839
You want me to run?

105
00:06:37,839 --> 00:06:39,160
Did you expect me to run?

106
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,639
Qian Qian.

107
00:06:43,079 --> 00:06:44,959
No, I mean Ms. Qian.

108
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,600
Listen.

109
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:49,160
You didn't tell me about this beforehand.

110
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:51,439
We didn't set the rules.

111
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:52,680
I get it now.

112
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,319
If I had known, I promise.

113
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:57,600
I would get here early no matter how busy I am.

114
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:00,399
Also,

115
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:03,399
I haven't run for years.

116
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:04,480
And I...

117
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:06,560
I currently have a lot of ailments.

118
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,600
It's true. I'm...

119
00:07:09,399 --> 00:07:10,839
Let's discuss this.

120
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:13,000
We'll decide on a new set of rules, okay?

121
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,839
You have ailments, do you?

122
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:18,839
Yes.

123
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:22,000
You'll feel better after running and sweating.

124
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,720
I'm the instructor.

125
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:25,000
I call the shots.

126
00:07:26,839 --> 00:07:27,879
Ms. Qian.

127
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,560
Well...

128
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:32,639
How about this?

129
00:07:33,199 --> 00:07:34,639
I'll pay for it.

130
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,319
One yuan per meter.

131
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,240
Mr. Hou.

132
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:41,600
Not everything can be bought with money.

133
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,519
I guess it's too low.

134
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:46,079
How about two yuan per meter?

135
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,879
I'll buy it, okay?

136
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:49,879
I'll count to three. If you don't run, I'm leaving.

137
00:07:49,879 --> 00:07:51,759
- One. - Fine.

138
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:53,560
I will run.

139
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,800
Right.

140
00:07:57,920 --> 00:08:00,040
This is a gift for you.

141
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,079
I hope you like it.

142
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:02,360
Run. Off you go!

143
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:53,210
This is the hotel of one of our employees.

144
00:08:53,210 --> 00:08:55,480
If you like the food here,

145
00:08:56,210 --> 00:08:57,360
you're welcome any time.

146
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,480
It's on me.

147
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,600
You're too kind.

148
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,960
Thank you, Lan Qi.

149
00:09:01,330 --> 00:09:03,039
Come over for dinner sometime.

150
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:04,840
- I'll cook for you. - All right.

151
00:09:06,090 --> 00:09:07,279
What about you, Mr. Wu?

152
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:08,559
I can give you a ride.

153
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:10,450
It's okay. You must be busy.

154
00:09:10,450 --> 00:09:11,639
I can go on my own. It's no trouble.

155
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:13,360
- Yes, let him go on his own. - All right.

156
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:14,759
See you, Mr. Wu, ma'am.

157
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:15,799
- Bye. - Bye.

158
00:09:44,039 --> 00:09:45,159
Hold on. I'm choking.

159
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:55,399
I haven't had an appetite like this in years.

160
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:56,960
Everything tastes good.

161
00:09:59,519 --> 00:10:02,759
Actually, going for a run is good.

162
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:06,090
It's a mission from Ms. Qian's mission.

163
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,799
I will do it to my best ability.

164
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,090
Did you see it?

165
00:10:10,090 --> 00:10:11,159
After running today,

166
00:10:11,159 --> 00:10:13,679
my golf skills were better than usual.

167
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,360
Looks like running...

168
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,840
is pretty good.

169
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:19,240
Are you planning to be late again?

170
00:10:19,799 --> 00:10:22,210
What's the matter? Are you addicted to running?

171
00:10:22,210 --> 00:10:23,240
That's right.

172
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:26,759
The point is, I tasted the reward for being a latecomer.

173
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:31,679
Running, sweating.

174
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:35,039
And I get to have a meal with Ms. Qian.

175
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,960
And do you know...

176
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,090
what the most important thing is?

177
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:42,399
I made you angry.

178
00:10:43,399 --> 00:10:44,759
When you're angry,

179
00:10:44,759 --> 00:10:46,210
the way your nostrils puff up,

180
00:10:46,210 --> 00:10:48,639
I don't know why, but it makes me gleeful.

181
00:10:51,330 --> 00:10:53,330
If you're late again,

182
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:55,639
the punishment might not be running.

183
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:59,919
I have plenty of ways to punish you.

184
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,159
What do you want?

185
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:03,519
I can't tell you now.

186
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,559
We'll decide when you're late.

187
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:07,080
Fine, you win.

188
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,240
You little brat.

189
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,879
I'm telling you.

190
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:11,200
I'm busy with work.

191
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,799
I tend to lose track of time when I'm working.

192
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:13,879
Next time,

193
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:16,080
could you remind me earlier?

194
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,120
All right?

195
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,080
A person...

196
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:21,440
only tends to forget things...

197
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,840
that they don't care about.

198
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,120
Okay. I'll keep that in mind.

199
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,840
I'll remember that.

200
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:35,639
Do you like the gift I gave you?

201
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,159
I totally forgot about it.

202
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,200
It's a good mask.

203
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,840
All my friends use it.

204
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,840
I'll keep it.

205
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:45,840
Sure.

206
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:49,159
I really like this bag.

207
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:50,919
But it's too much.

208
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,279
I can't accept it.

209
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:54,120
- But... - Okay.

210
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:55,759
It's almost time.

211
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,919
Thank you for the mask. Bye.

212
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,360
Qian...

213
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,000
Come in.

214
00:12:47,639 --> 00:12:48,639
Dad.

215
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:53,600
I made coffee for you to try.

216
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,320
What are you doing?

217
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:04,480
It's nothing. I just wanted you to try my handiwork.

218
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:17,159
I guess the sun will rise from the west.

219
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:30,080
How is it?

220
00:13:31,159 --> 00:13:32,399
Smooth.

221
00:13:33,039 --> 00:13:34,120
It's good.

222
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:36,519
My dad knows what he's doing.

223
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:44,039
When I was younger,

224
00:13:45,519 --> 00:13:48,000
every time I was rushing to complete a design,

225
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,360
night and day all melded together.

226
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:51,240
I drank coffee like no tomorrow.

227
00:13:51,639 --> 00:13:53,240
But I can't anymore. I'm old now.

228
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:55,720
I get heart palpitations if I drink coffee.

229
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,960
It has been hard on you.

230
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,480
Out with it.

231
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,799
What is it you want from me?

232
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:04,960
It's nothing. It's really nothing.

233
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,759
Let Wu Shi Yi come back.

234
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:09,799
It's not that Zhou Quan is bad.

235
00:14:09,799 --> 00:14:11,559
He's very good at his job.

236
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:15,080
However, Shi Yi got fired...

237
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:17,080
because she was framed.

238
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:19,120
It's the right thing to do.

239
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:21,960
Let's at least complete the contract period.

240
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:22,960
Am I right?

241
00:14:26,519 --> 00:14:29,480
In order to let a bodyguard fulfill her contract period,

242
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:33,039
you've learned to talk nicely to your dad?

243
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,320
That's surprising to me.

244
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,000
Isn't that normal?

245
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:40,000
All right.

